snippet: Tynice Martin and Lanay Montgomery each scored 16 points, Montgomery with 10 rebounds and five blocked shots, as unbeaten and 13th-ranked West Virginia defeated Mount St. Mary's 77-45 on Wednesday night....
lead_paragraph: Tynice Martin and Lanay Montgomery each scored 16 points, Montgomery with 10 rebounds and five blocked shots, as unbeaten and 13th-ranked West Virginia defeated Mount St. Mary's 77-45 on Wednesday night.

headline.main: Martin, Montgomery Keep No. 13 W. Virginia Women Unbeaten
